nde2.types.delivery

Class Dataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • nde2.types.NDE2Result
      • nde2.types.delivery.Dataset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Dataset
extends NDE2Result
    This class represents a dataset returned by the delivery service. It contains topics, values and boundaries relevant to the dataset.

    filip

        public Dataset(int datasetCode,
       String creator,
       String description,
       String subjectCategory,
       String title,
       Map<Integer,Topic> topics,
       Map<Integer,Period> periods,
       Map<Integer,Boundary> boundaries,
       List<DataSetItem> items)
        Parameters:
        datasetCode - Internal identifier of the dataset in question. This will be the same as a familyId of a DataSetFamiliy
        creator - Creator of the data set. Use to do attributions for data.
        description - Description of the data set. May be empty.
        subjectCategory - Subject category of the data set. May be empty.
        title - Title of the data set.
        topics - A list of topics covered by the data set.
        periods - A list of periods covered by the data set.
        boundaries - A list of geographical boundaries covered by the data set.
        items - A list of values in the data set.
